title: What's more likely: Packers or Cowboys making the playoffs?
itunes:title: What's more likely: Packers or Cowboys making the playoffs?
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Colleen Wolfe- recap the thrilling Monday Night Football matchup between the Patriots and Dolphins, which resulted in a surprising upset for the Pats (4:00); A look at news from around the league, including Carson Wentz's season-ending injury- a premonition Colleen had earlier in the season (16:00); A fan-favorite segment returns- "What's More Likely" (28:00), which includes possible playoff scenarios, coach firings and of course, a mythical creature reference from Sessler.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
